author: wangyongyi@pku.edu.cn

This repository provides NFG (normal form game) analytical tools, which decompose a NFG into Harmonic, Potential and Non-strategic components.

For the definition of Harmonic, Potential and Non-strategic components, please refer to

"Flows and Decompositions of Games, Harmonic and Potential Games" 
MIT, Parblo A. Parrilo, Ozan Candogan, Ishai Menache, Asu Ozdag. ICIAM 2011
